Diary of Lydia:

Twenty-fourth day of Shilen.


Fast deliver my invitation to Nidrah, and it took far too easy!

I had been prepared in such a hurry when he arrives! I had to make thousands of mistakes, but he nirazu nepozhalovalsya! He was too nice? Or maybe he just does not care!

He told me that was the case here; and this case is nothing neimeet obshego with our family.
